Usage: changeBBoxMasterToR0 [-help] [<cellName>] [-checkOnly]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<cellName>            # Specifies that cell, or the list of blackbox cells,
                      # whose orientation will be converted to R0.
                      # (string, optional)
-checkOnly            # Specifies that the command will not actually convert
                      # the orientation of any master blackbox. (bool, optional)